    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), powered by a 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing. This M96 engine is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a visceral connection to the rear-wheel-drive layout. The car features a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently serviced cooling system with updated water pump and low-temp thermostat. Suspension remains firm with no bushing play, maintaining the precision of the factory multi-link rear geometry. Braking is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing minimal lip. A true enthusiast's specimen with a clean rev range and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
