    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2016 BMW M3 in Alpine White over Sakhir Orange Extended Merino Leather is a stunning example of a driver-focused machine. Meticulously maintained and garage-kept, the exterior retains a deep, glossy luster with only minor stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the carbon fiber trim is flawless, and the heated leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. Mechanically, this M3 is turn-key. It features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and has been serviced exclusively at certified intervals, with a recent brake fluid flush and oil service performed just 500 miles ago. Riding on Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with plenty of life remaining, it delivers a tight, responsive handling profile that feels as precise as the day it left the showroom. This is a complete, honest vehicle ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
